-1.bio: There is something you must always remember. You are braver than you believe, stronger than you seem, and smarter than you think.
-1.name: Gregory Hansell

0.bio: Hi I'm Greg. My favorite holiday is Easter. I like to climb, ski, code, and use the oxford comma. I once tried to do all four at simultaneously and broke my laptop.
0.name: Gregory Hansell

1.bio: Ouch! That hurt, don't touch me again.
1.name: Gregory Hansell

6.bio: Seriously, knock it off! Don't make me come out of this machine.
6.name: Gregory Hansell
